Package: easysplash-swrender
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: EasySplash
 This is a simple program for animated splash screens using OpenGL ES for rendering. It consists of the main splash screen program (easysplash) and a small control program (easysplashctl).